! Welcome to Hiki
This is FrontPage of [[Hiki|http://hikiwiki.org/en/]].
If you can see this page, the installation completed successfully, perhaps ;-)

! Before starting (IMPORTANT)
Choose [Admin] menu and set password for the administrator.
Only an administrator can freeze pages (this means `only an administrator can update')
and cancel frozen state.

! Format of Hiki
Format of Hiki is similar to the original one. So you can easily write if you know
original wiki's format. However, some format is extended originally.
See TextFormattingRules for details.